{"tid":2486963,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"何厚鏵女兒6750萬購中半山豪宅呎價約4.5萬","createTime":"2021-04-13T08:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T15:24:46.000Z","uid":73269,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f498181d1ecf2fa46a8d47614fc8b8237b549fd2","tid":2486963,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:39:12.000Z","msg":"據土地註冊處資料顯示，中半山帝景園4座高層B室，於上月19日以6750萬成交，買家以個人名義何美芝(HO MEI CHEE CHARMAINE)登記，與澳門前特首、全國政協副主席何厚鏵的女兒中英文名字相同。原業主於1991年以564萬購入，<strong><ins><span class=\"red\">持貨30年間帳面獲利6186萬，期間升值約11倍</span></ins></strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同區代理指，上址面積1513方呎，為3房間隔，以易手價計，每呎造價約4.5萬。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/1545289/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F1545289%2F&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DOQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=bca673ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F1545289%2F&h=93b67ee4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/1545289/</a>"},{"pid":"43c4bbf63482385a063b2fa476ea67d2dbb4d935","tid":2486963,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:39:38.000Z","msg":"錢從何以來？"},{"pid":"0dfc0627bb2bb2bbed23bec47ae616b6838f6c7e","tid":2486963,"uid":158499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43c4bbf63482385a063b2fa476ea67d2dbb4d935","tid":2486963,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:39:38.000Z","msg":"錢從何以來？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:40:03.000Z","msg":"不嬲四大家族"},{"pid":"1f37615823ed859e25e13769b46176a3ab021f6d","tid":2486963,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43c4bbf63482385a063b2fa476ea67d2dbb4d935","tid":2486963,"uid":